github.com/feketemihai\n    ```\n---\n\n# Romania - Stock Report (Fi\u0219\u0103 Magazie)\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:6d1391824351ad8e2e2feb485c5ae2bf1a3451aefb62df00604c71284a628dfa\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module adds a stock report according to Romanian requirements.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Installation\n\nTo install this module, you need to:\n\n- clone the branch 15.0 of the repository\n  <https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania>\n- add the path to this repository in your configuration (addons-path)\n- update the module list\n- search for \"Romania - Stock Report\" in your addons\n- install the module\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_ro_stock_report%0Aversion:%2018.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Terrabit\n- NextERP Romania\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Terrabit](https://www.terrabit.ro):\n\n  - Dorin Hongu \\<<mailto:dhongu@gmail.com>>\n\n- [NextERP Romania](https://www.nexterp.ro):\n\n  - Fekete Mihai \\<<mailto:feketemihai@nexterp.ro>>\n  - Alexandru Teodor \\<<mailto:teodoralexandru@nexterp.ro>>\n  - Musat Natanaela \\<<mailto:musatnatanaela@nexterp.ro>>\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with\ntechnical issues.\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainers](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-dhongu }} {{ maintainer-feketemihai }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-romania](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/tree/18.0/l10n_ro_stock_report) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report.tests.test_report_stock", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report.tests..test_report_stock", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report.report", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report..report", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report.report", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report.report.stock_report", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report.report..stock_report", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report.__manifest__", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_stock_report.tests.test_report_stock", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2020 Terrabit", "License AGPL-3.0